*+
*  Name:
*     ARD_PAR

*  Purpose:
*     Define ARD system parameter constants.

*  Language:
*     Starlink Fortran 77

*  Type of Module:
*     Global constants include file.

*  Description:
*     This file defines parameters affecting the sizes of
*     ARD buffers. It should only be used by routines using ARD
*     facilities.

*  Authors:
*     PDRAPER: Peter Draper (STARLINK)
*     {enter_new_authors_here}

*  History:
*     7-OCT-1991 (PDRAPER):
*        Original version.
*     {enter_changes_here}

*  Bugs:
*     {note_any_bugs_here}

*-

*  Global constants:

*  Maximum line length of extracted line.
      INTEGER ARD__MAXLEN
      PARAMETER ( ARD__MAXLEN = 1024 )

*  Number of keywords recognised by ARD.
      INTEGER ARD__MAXKEY
      PARAMETER ( ARD__MAXKEY = 9 )

*  Maximum length of keyword strings.
      INTEGER ARD__KEYLEN
      PARAMETER ( ARD__KEYLEN = 7 )

*  Maximum number of dimensions
      INTEGER ARD__MAXDIM
      PARAMETER ( ARD__MAXDIM = 7 )
* $Id$
